        <cite>— Verified Buyer</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <div style="text-align:center; margin: 40px 0;">
        <a href="https://hnrqqt-an.myshopify.com/products/e-bike-security-bundle" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 1.15rem; padding: 16px 48px; display: inline-block; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px;">Buy Now — $89 <s style="opacity:0.6; font-size:0.85rem;">$110</s></a>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">Free shipping · 30-day returns · 2-year warranty</p>
